  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a standard action, you can make a melee touch attack that causes a living creature to become&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Shaken\" rel=\"nofollow\">shaken</a>&nbsp;for a number of rounds equal to 1/2 your wizard level (minimum 1). If you touch a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Shaken\" rel=\"nofollow\">shaken</a>&nbsp;creature with this ability, it becomes&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Frightened\" rel=\"nofollow\">frightened</a>&nbsp;for 1 round if it has fewer Hit Dice than your wizard level. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Intelligence-Int-\" rel=\"nofollow\">Intelligence</a>&nbsp;modifier.</p>",
